==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Taskmaster
<hw>Task"mas`ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who imposes a
task, or burdens another with labor; one whose duty is to assign tasks;
an overseer.</def> <rj><au>Ex. i. 11.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>All is, if I have grace to use it so,⟦br⟧
As ever in my great <qex>Taskmaster's</qex> eye.</q>
<rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Task wage</ent>⟦br⟧
